title: And Lips That We Might Tell
description: Dangerfield is called in to assist the police when a lorry is hijacked, a passing driver is killed, and the lorry driver (and only surviving witness) is severely concussed. Outside work, preparations are underway for his daughter Ali's wedding.

title: Tying the Knot
description: The wedding day of Dr. Paige and Gillian Cramer gets ruined when she gets involved saving a young boys life, and they both put work first. Cramer decides to leave him and everyone's sad.
